a selfie holding a valid ID/Drivers License. The ID must be fully visible to read.
Must be at least 18 years of age.
Large amounts of $1, $5, $10 are not accepted, Do your best to pay with bigger bills.
Online Banking like Cashapp, Venmo, Zelle and ApplePay are not accepted.

Once you place your order you will be given an address with instructions on how to enter the parking ramp. There is a $5.00 fee that can only be paid on a Debit/Credit Card. Pick up orders are recommended for people who want to pick up on their own time and not have to wait for a delivery.

You can place your order anytime of the day. Shop opens at 2:00pm Monday-Saturday and that is when you can expect a reply back. The cut off time to order for a delivery is 3:00pm, the driver leaves right after and we do not carry extras. The address you give us needs to be an address you will be waiting at. Its like waiting for the mailman to show up, we will let you know once we are heading towards your direction. Typical delivery times can be from 3:00pm-8:00pm depending on where you are located during the route. We only deliver to the Twin Cities area. If you are outside our range you will have to pick your order up or have it mailed.
The cut off time to order for a delivery is 3pm (deliveries start after and we do not carry extras).
Have your cash in your hands before messaging an order (this makes everything go much smoother).
No Minimum for pick up orders.
